  "summary": {
    "en": "A 100-piece STEM fort kit for colorful house frames, group play, and retail-ready creative building.",
    "zh": "100件STEM堡垒拼搭套装，适合彩色房屋框架、多人互动和零售化创意建构。"
  },
  "description": {
    "en": [
      "The 100-piece set supports house frames, play tents, and simple architectural structures for home and classroom activities.",
      "Colorful rods and connector balls help children recognize patterns, build sequences, and experiment with balance.",
      "Actual packed components make the set practical for retail display, sampling review, and production confirmation.",
      "The flat color-box format is convenient for shipping stacks, gift channels, and OEM/ODM packaging updates."
    ],
    "zh": [
      "100件套可支持房屋框架、游戏帐篷和简单建筑结构，适合家庭与课堂活动。",
      "彩色杆件和连接球帮助儿童识别规律、建立拼接顺序并尝试平衡结构。",
      "实际包装组件清晰，便于零售备货、样品核对和生产确认。",
      "扁盒彩盒形式便于运输堆叠、礼品渠道和OEM/ODM包装调整。"
    ]
  },
